{"tid":785640,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你四海咖哩魚蛋","createTime":"2018-08-19T11:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T12:37:19.000Z","uid":125213,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4b34fc409473ebfca0de0d3a7577d59ab46b759","tid":785640,"uid":125213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:19:34.000Z","msg":"早幾日食咗包四海咖哩魚蛋 一放入口 酸既 lur都lur唔切<br />\n一開始仲以為係放雪櫃太耐變壞(雖然淨係放咗幾日)<br />\n頭先又買左包 屌你老未 都係有浸酸味<br />\n依家四海咖哩魚蛋啲料變cheap又變味 仲要一蚊一粒 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b086b1ad3668a7d11a5e3d13eb6b6268e2d35fb0","tid":785640,"uid":17646,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:23:08.000Z","msg":"報食環啦<br />\n睇下係賣個間野存儲有問題定四海製造或運輸出事"},{"pid":"43b2d835f6e9f02f5ef77c3fbe2d8041e8f3f2f0","tid":785640,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"聯絡區議員同民間組織，搵多d受害人，人數夠500人就可以先開記招講述事件，跟手集體去政總交請願信，促使政府加強監管。"},{"pid":"36a96d84bba7d924f5a6d90f23df1718f0092f92","tid":785640,"uid":144224,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"前幾日食完 覺得冇異味喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36164ed5dbd296a04def91f6cb0167491109ec7a","tid":785640,"uid":202354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"有可能係運輸問題，你可以試下去另一間超市買多一包黎試，睇下仲有冇怪酸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}